        " السِّوَاكُ يَذْهَبُ بِالدَّمْعَةِ وَ يَجْلُو الْبَصَرَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Fazzal, from Hammad Bin Isa, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The brushing of teeth removes the tears and polishes the vision’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "7. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn Faddal from Hammad ibn ‘Isa who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Tooth brushing stops tears and sharpens eyesight.’” "
        ]
      }
